OL,4,CNationwide tells 13,000 staff to 'work
OL,5,Canywhere'
OL,6, Nationwide is to allow 13,000 office
OL,7, staff to choose where they work under a
OL,8, new flexibility scheme.
OL,10,FThe UK's biggest building society said
OL,11,Fits "work anywhere" plan will allow
OL,12,Femployees more control of their lives.
OL,14,FUnder the plan, Nationwide is closing
OL,15,Fthree offices in Swindon, with 3,000
OL,16,Fstaff either moving to the nearby HQ,
OL,17,Fworking from home, or mixing the two.
OL,19,FOther UK staff may be able to work from
OL,20,Ftheir local High Street branch if they
OL,21,Fprefer, rather than travel to offices.
